26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_ramgm107.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "ram.h"
30
31static const struct nvkm_ram_func
32gm107_ram_func = {
33 .init = gk104_ram_init,
34 .get = gf100_ram_get,
35 .put = gf100_ram_put,
36};
37
38int
39gm107_ram_new(struct nvkm_fb *fb, struct nvkm_ram **pram)
40{
41 if (!(*pram = kzalloc(sizeof(**pram), GFP_KERNEL)))
42 return -ENOMEM;
43
44 return gf100_ram_ctor(&gm107_ram_func, fb, 0x021c14, *pram);
45}
